      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.247-2</ph> Permits, Authorities, or Franchises.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3680e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="47.207-1.dita#FAR_47_207_1"
                     base="i1070991"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">47.207-1</xref>(a)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Permits, Authorities, or Franchises (Jan 1997)</p>
         <ol id="d3636e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3680e19">
                  <ph platform="hide" props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The offeror does <cite outputclass="Checkbox"
                        xtrc="52.247-2_d29e23"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="VFI">□</cite>, does not <cite outputclass="Checkbox"
                        xtrc="52.247-2_d29e26"
                        class="- topic/cite "
                        xtrf="VFI">□</cite>, hold authorization from the Federal Highway Administration (FHWA) or other cognizant regulatory body. If authorization is held, it is as follows:</p>
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3680e29">
                  <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrf="VFI"
                        xtrc="52.247-2_qvf_kzt_21c"
                        class="- topic/cite ">__________________________________________________ (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Name of regulatory body</i>)</cite>
               </p>
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3680e34">
                  <cite outputclass="SingleLine"
                        xtrf="VFI"
                        xtrc="52.247-2_klr_nzt_21c"
                        class="- topic/cite ">__________________________________________________ (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Authorization No.</i>)</cite>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3680e40">
                  <ph platform="hide" props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The offeror shall furnish to the Government, if requested, copies of the authorization before moving the material under any contract awarded. In addition, the offeror shall, at the offeror’s expense, obtain and maintain any permits, franchises, licenses, and other authorities issued by State and local governments.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
